** TODO Essential Commands to Internalize
- [X] Files: C-x C-f (open), C-x C-s (save), C-x C-w (save as)
- [X] Buffers: C-x b (switch), C-x C-b (list all), C-x k (kill)
- [X] Windows: C-x 2 (split H), C-x 3 (split V), C-x 1 (close others), C-x 0 (close this)
- [X] Movement: C-n/C-p (lines), C-f/C-b (chars), M-f/M-b (words), C-a/C-e (line start/end)
- [X] Search: C-s (forward), C-r (backward)
- [X] Undo: C-/ or C-x u

** TODO Registers (Your Clipboard Palette)
- [ ] Store text: select region, C-x r s <letter>
- [ ] Insert text: C-x r i <letter>
- [ ] Store position: C-x r SPC <letter>
- [ ] Jump to position: C-x r j <letter>
- [ ] Practice: store 3 snippets, insert them

** TODO Bookmarks (Persistent Locations)
- [X] Set bookmark: C-x r m
- [X] Jump to bookmark: C-x r b
- [X] List all bookmarks: C-x r l
- [ ] Delete bookmark: M-x bookmark-delete

** TODO Abbrevs (Text Expansion)
- [ ] Define abbrev: M-x define-global-abbrev
- [ ] View all: M-x edit-abbrevs
- [ ] Save abbrevs: M-x write-abbrev-file
- [ ] Test: define "sig" -> your signature, type sig<space>

